description:
Does the MK5 come with CarPlay? Can I use the Mark 5 with an iPhone?  Can I connect my MK5 to the iPhone?  The MK5 is an Android device what if I have an Apple iPhone?

SIMPLE ANSWER: YES, CARPLAY WORKS, WIRED AND WIRELESSLY!!  In this video, I cover setup, and briefly demo CarPlay working via the Zlink App on the AuCar Mark 5.  You can assume the same works on the Phoenix MK3 and other Android T-screens too.

Buy the AuCar MK5 here: https://squarewheelsauto.com/b2b1w
USE COUPON CODE: SQUAREWHEELS to save $50 at checkout!

The all-new MARK 6 is now available for sale!
BUY NOW:
https://squarewheelsauto.com/products/new-aucar-mark6-tesla-style-screen-for-infiniti-q50-q60-mk6

Stay tuned, install and review vids coming soon.

Alternate link: this MK5 clone is available for a bit more on Amazon, if you want 2-day shipping:
https://amzn.to/3EvKunt

DIY MARK 5/TESLA SCREEN  INSTALLATION: 
https://youtu.be/Imqw7oa3izE

HIT ME ON IG:

square@square-built.com

0:00 - YES, CarPlay works on the AuCar Mark 5
